Draconians are an artificial race created ages ago when bizarre, 
ancient magicks were used to adapt unhatched dragonets into 
humanoid form.  They retain the vast intellect of their dragon 
ancestors and much of the strength as well, but their strange 
appearance has hampered their acceptance as a race until just 
recently.  Physically, they are about the same height as humans, but 
there the similarity ends.  They have scales of varying shades, as 
well as a tail and vestigial wings.  Their eyes have slitted pupils, like 
a reptile or a cat.

Draconians have a special breath attack they may use periodically using
the breath command.
 
Draconians cannot join the following guilds:  Bard, Charlatan, Cleric of
Mitra, Druid, Garou, Paladin.
